## Description {#details}

A switch()-like statement whose cases are string literals.

The <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringswitch">StringSwitch</a> class is a simple form of a switch() statement that determines whether the given string matches one of the given string literals. The template type parameter <code>T</code> is the type of the value that will be returned from the string-switch expression. For example, the following code switches on the name of a color in <code>argv</code>&#91;i&#93;:


<ProgramListing>

<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight"><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/anonymous-aarch64a57fploadbalancing-cpp-/#afcb9ac67c90816f55d217d4f629e1047">Color</a> color = <a href="#acb567c28ed2b00f93894c700dab8faea">StringSwitch&lt;Color&gt;</a>(argv&#91;i&#93;)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Case(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;red&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, Red)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Case(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;orange&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, Orange)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Case(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;yellow&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, Yellow)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Case(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;green&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, Green)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Case(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;blue&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, Blue)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Case(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;indigo&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, Indigo)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Cases(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;violet&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, </span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;purple&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, Violet)</span></CodeLine>
<CodeLine><span class="doxyHighlight">  .Default(UnknownColor);</span></CodeLine>

</ProgramListing>
